{
    "title": "Modification Technique",
    "description": "Schema for submitting an information on genetic modification technique.",
    "id": "/profiles/modification_technique.json",
    "$schema": "http://json-schema.org/draft-04/schema#",
    "type": "object",
    "required": ["lab", "award", "source"],
    "identifyingProperties": ["uuid","aliases"],
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "mixinProperties": [
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/schema_version" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/uuid" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/aliases" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/attribution" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/standard_status" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/submitted" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/product_id" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/source" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/notes" },
        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/documents" }
    ],
    "properties": {
        "schema_version": {
            "hidden comment": "Bump the default in the subclasses."
        },

        "vectors": {
            "description": "Vector(s) used to perform the genetic modification.",
            "type": "array",
            "default": [],
            "uniqueItems": true,
            "items": {
     

    WE have to RETHINK vector to point out to ADDGENE
    ON the other hand if lab performed modification to the vector - shouldwe require submission to ADDGENE?
    ONE OF THE options is to add VECTOR object that will be minimal CONSTRUCT version and keep an array of these here.

         
                    "description": "Vector details.",
                    "type": "object",
                    "additionalProperties": false,
                    "mixinProperties": [
                        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/aliases" },
                        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/product_id" },
                        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/source" },
                        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/notes" },
                        { "$ref": "mixins.json#/documents" }
                    ],
                    "properties": {
                        "vector_backbone_name":{
                            "title": "Backbone name",
                            "description": "The name of the vector backbone used for the modification.",
                            "type": "string"
                        },
                        "promoter_used": {
                            "title": "Promoter used on the vector",
                            "description": "The name of the gene that the promoter regulates natively.",
                            "comment": "See target.json for available identifiers.",
                            "type": "string",
                            "linkTo": "Target"
                        },
                        "url":{
                            "title": "URL",
                            "description": "An external resource with additional information about the vector.",
                            "type": "string",
                            "format": "uri"
                        }
                    }
                }              
            }
        }
    }
} 